@Host = https://localhost:7025
@Email = admin@restaurante.com
@Senha = Admin@123

### 1) Registrar
POST {{Host}}/api/Auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nomeCompleto": "Teste Final",
  "email": "{{Email}}",
  "password": "{{Senha}}"
}

### 2) Login (copie o token da resposta)
POST {{Host}}/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{Email}}",
  "password": "{{Senha}}"
}

### 3) Criar item de cardápio (usar Bearer token)
POST {{Host}}/api/cardapio
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..9pGvdNg4W2kvoK5PbCgVBnnW2uAJhmXxGc3vfh-Gtdo

{
  "nome": "Frango Grelhado Especial",
  "descricao": "Frango com legumes e arroz",
  "precoBase": 42.90,
  "periodo": "Jantar",
  "ativo": true
}

### 4) Listar cardápio jantar
GET {{Host}}/api/cardapio?periodo=Jantar

### 5) Vincular ingredientes no item (trocar {itemId} e IDs)
POST {{Host}}/api/cardapio/1/ingredientes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..9pGvdNg4W2kvoK5PbCgVBnnW2uAJhmXxGc3vfh-Gtdo

{
  "ingredienteIds": [1, 2]
}

### 6) Criar pedido
POST {{Host}}/api/pedidos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..9pGvdNg4W2kvoK5PbCgVBnnW2uAJhmXxGc3vfh-Gtdo

{
  "periodo": "Jantar",
  "tipoAtendimento": "DeliveryAplicativo",
  "nomeAplicativo": "iFood",
  "enderecoEntrega": "Rua A, 123",
  "itens": [
    { "itemCardapioId": 41, "quantidade": 2 }
  ]
}

### 7) Meus pedidos
GET {{Host}}/api/pedidos/meus
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..9pGvdNg4W2kvoK5PbCgVBnnW2uAJhmXxGc3vfh-Gtdo

### 8) Detalhe do pedido (trocar id)
GET {{Host}}/api/pedidos/6
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..9pGvdNg4W2kvoK5PbCgVBnnW2uAJhmXxGc3vfh-Gtdo

### 9) Atualizar status do pedido
PATCH {{Host}}/api/pedidos/6/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..9pGvdNg4W2kvoK5PbCgVBnnW2uAJhmXxGc3vfh-Gtdo

{
  "status": "Confirmado"
}

### 10) Criar reserva
POST {{Host}}/api/reservas
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..9pGvdNg4W2kvoK5PbCgVBnnW2uAJhmXxGc3vfh-Gtdo

{
  "dataHora": "2026-03-29T19:30:00",
  "numerMesa": 10,
  "numeroPessoas": 2
}

### 11) Minhas reservas
GET {{Host}}/api/reservas/minhas
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..9pGvdNg4W2kvoK5PbCgVBnnW2uAJhmXxGc3vfh-Gtdo

### 12) Cancelar reserva (trocar id)
PATCH {{Host}}/api/reservas/5/cancelar
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..9pGvdNg4W2kvoK5PbCgVBnnW2uAJhmXxGc3vfh-Gtdo

### 13) Relatório: faturamento por atendimento
GET {{Host}}/api/relatorios/faturamento-por-atendimento?inicio=2026-03-01T00:00:00&fim=2026-03-31T23:59:59
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..Fu4pEMVWrrQOVewkURZ9nwTn42jy8VSuEezBNBrPXLw

### 14) Relatório: itens mais vendidos
GET {{Host}}/api/relatorios/itens-mais-vendidos?inicio=2026-03-01T00:00:00&fim=2026-03-31T23:59:59
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..Fu4pEMVWrrQOVewkURZ9nwTn42jy8VSuEezBNBrPXLw 

